Great golf. Great amenities. Amazing people.
We are known for our friendliness, casual atmosphere and engaging membership.
Coral Ridge is a Club like no other. We excel in bringing people together, creating memories that last a lifetime and being a cornerstone in the community. We are that sacred oasis for our Members and their families.

Begin Mini-Page 576098
Just for Kids
End Mini-Page 576098
Begin Mini-Page 575878
Kiddos are welcome, families applaud!
Finally, a place where parents AND their children can PLAY, make friends and enjoy the great outdoors.
At any given time, you'll see little ones horsing around on the playground or running the bases in an impromptu kickball game on the grassy area beside it. When it comes to structured fun; we've also got you covered! From junior golf and tennis clinics to outdoor movie nights on the green, dress-up character brunches and pool parties, cooking class, and more . . . we have oodles of ways for kids to be active and safe while having fun at the Club. It's good old fashioned fun with friends!
End Mini-Page 575878

Begin Mini-Page 575596
Summer Camps & Clinics
End Mini-Page 575596
Begin Mini-Page 575880
Kids love our GOLF, TENNIS and SWIM programs and clinics!
For over 40 years, Coral Ridge Country Club has provided exceptional Golf, Tennis and Swim junior experiences for Members and children of the community. Experienced professionals and instructors provide individualized attention helping children to learn, improve and gain confidence in a sport while having FUN. Games, prizes and competitions emphasize the instructional goals.
After-school programs are offered throughout the school year and summer programs are offered from June to mid-August. Members and non-Members are welcome to attend our programs and clinics.
SUMMER CAMPS
End Mini-Page 575880

Lifestyle & Amenities
End Mini-Page 576097
Begin Mini-Page 575838
A Foodie's Dream & Events that WOW
Chef Udo's eclectic menu offerings will pamper your palate, whether you're enjoying a standard lunch on our beautiful terrace or joining us for one of our decadent wine dinners.
For happy hours and socializing, the sunken clubhouse bar area is one of our Member's preferred gathering places. But, considering the unobstructed view of a sunset over the golf course, the Terrace is also a great place for drinks and a relaxing dinner.
End Mini-Page 575838

End Mini-Page 575551
Begin Mini-Page 575552
We know how to celebrate
Our EVENTS are the talk of the town!
Coral Ridge knows how to bring family and friends together. Whether it is Winter Wonderland with ice skating and 10 tons of snow, to our dazzling dinner shows and tournament receptions. Holidays are also a must at the Club. For an ultra casual meal, Members visit our outdoor Carousel snack bar. Whatever your fancy, you'll find it here!
End Mini-Page 575552

Begin Mini-Page 575556
Tennis
For the LOVE of the Game
Regardless of your level of play or experience, we've got a program for you! The Club boasts 11 first-class clay tennis courts touted as the best maintained in the county, all lighted for night play. Will Hoag, resident USPTA Hall-of-Famer, and his team of professionals have the experience and expertise to help you with your game. Whether you're looking for private lessons, competitive team play, junior clinics, or simply a fun group to play with, we will happily introduce you to the Members and programs that best match your needs.
End Mini-Page 575556

Begin Mini-Page 575846
Pool
Fun in the SUN for Everyone
As a Member of Coral Ridge Country Club you will have unlimited use of the 25-yard swimming pool where you can bring guests as often as you like. Our Pool is the ideal place for our year-round pool parties, catered birthday celebrations, swim lessons and water exercises. Come eat lunch poolside, swim a lap in our heated pool, or simply sunbathe while the kids enjoy the water and poolside play area. Ping pong, foosball and pool toys are provided. Bring your suit and we’ll provide the rest!
End Mini-Page 575846

Begin Mini-Page 575768
A Landmark Legacy
Nestled in the heart of Fort Lauderdale...
and just minutes to the beach, Members find space to unwind, room to breathe, good friends and laughter all around. Exceptional golf is the cornerstone of the only golf and country club in town...complemented by remarkable dining, superior tennis, swimming and events to delight everyone in the family.
Founded in 1954, the Club boasts an 18-hole, Robert Trent Jones, Sr., classically designed golf course, recently restored by his son Rees Jones and a 9-hole Par 3 course also designed by Rees Jones. In addition to two meticulously maintained courses and various golf practice facilities, the Club has 11 flawless tennis courts, a junior Olympic swimming pool, playground, snack bar, and Clubhouse with Terrace dining.
We are a private, non-equity club that has become the core of the community and are known for our genuine friendliness, casual atmosphere and engaging membership. Along with our amenities, the staff and management team are truly what set the Club apart. The first-class service you will experience while at the Club can be summed up in our
Welcome H.O.M.E.
motto in which
Hospitable People
and
Outstanding Servic
e
lead to
Memorable Experiences
that
Exceed Expectations
.
End Mini-Page 575768
